# ⚠️  SECURITY WARNING: NEVER COMMIT SENSITIVE DATA
# This file ensures that secrets, API keys, and credentials are NOT pushed to Git
# If you accidentally commit secrets, use: git rm --cached <filename> && git commit -m "Remove secrets"
# Then rotate your tokens/keys immediately!

